Subject: Design 
Software: Illustrator 
Author: Mordy Golding 

Give the gift of illustration: learn to draw a wedding monogram in Illustrator. Mordy Golding shares his insights on taking a design from hand-drawn sketch into a polished piece of vector art. Using the techniques shown in these videos, you can follow along with Mordy's heritage-based design or create a custom monogram of your own. The finished piece can be used on wedding websites, invitations, foil and embossing dies, stamps, and more.
